    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine runs reliably and the transmission shifts through all gears, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a slight suspension creak over bumps. Externally, the paint has some fading on the hood and several noticeable door dings and scratches. The interior is functional but has some wear on the driver's seat upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone needing basic transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
