      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, preserved in an impeccable state that transcends the standard used-market offering. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, exhibiting a level of care and maintenance that aligns with showroom standards. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as an investment-grade asset. We invite you to experience a vehicle of unrivaled distinction.",
