    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage its whole life. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
