    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade example, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, recently protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin is an oasis of perfection; the premium leather remains supple and taut without a single crease, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. I have curated a comprehensive binder containing every service record, documenting preventative maintenance performed well ahead of manufacturer intervals. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of road wear or inclement weather exposure. For the discerning buyer who demands a 'no-stories' vehicle, this is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
