      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute beauty! It has been my pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible, pristine shape\u2014you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've pampered this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that feels practically brand new, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
