    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. The chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul using Beisan components. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and original dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. A true turn-key enthusiast example with documented service history.",
